Codes: K - kernel route, C - connected, A - attached-host,
       S - static, O - OSPFv3, B - BGP, T - Table,
       > - selected route, * - FIB route, q - queued route, r - rejected route, b - backup

       t - trapped, o - offload failure

VRF default:
K>*  fd00::/80 [0/1024] (2) (0) is directly connected, docker0, 01w1d00h

VRF mgmt:
C>*  fe80::/64 (8) (0) is directly connected, eth0, 01w1d00h
